You may want to add this config to RPM stock patches:

    @PROP[RasterPropMonitorBasicMFD]:NEEDS[RasterPropMonitor,!MechJeb2]
    {@MODULE[RasterPropMonitor]{	!PAGE[smartass]{}}
    }

It removes the SmartAss page, so the button goes straight to the stock autopilot, if <abbr title="Mechjeb (mod)">MJ</abbr> is not installed
